---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import quote from "../assets/images/quote-icon.png";
import tommySuharto from "../assets/images/hutomo-mandala-putra.png";
---

<section
  class="px-[16px] md:px-[64px] lg:px-[80px] py-[64px] md:py-[80px] bg-white"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    <!-- LEFT QUOTE -->
    <div class="relative">
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-[16px] md:text-[17px] mb-6">
        Since its establishment, BAPP has focused on building a resilient fuel
        supply platform supported by experienced leadership and next-generation
        operational management. Through multiple market cycles, the company has
        strengthened its supply chain network and strategic positioning to
        support Indonesia’s industrial and marine growth.
      </p>
      <Image src={quote} alt="quote icon" class="w-12 h-12" />

      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-[16px] md:text-[17px] mb-3">
        “Operational discipline, supply reliability, and structured governance
        form the foundation of our fuel distribution operations across
        Indonesia.”
      </p>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <Image
          src={tommySuharto}
          alt="Hutomo Mandala Putra"
          class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover"
        />
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Hutomo Mandala Putra</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">President Director</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT CARD -->
    <div class="bg-[#018FF5] text-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-lg">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Our Journey</h3>

      <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4 text-white/90">
        Founded in 2004, BAPP began as a focused fuel supply operator serving
        selected industrial clients. Over time, the company expanded its
        operational footprint to serve marine, offshore, and mining sectors,
        supported by improved logistics systems and supply infrastructure.
      </p>

      <p class="leading-relaxed mb-6 text-white/90">
        TToday, BAPP operates with structured governance oversight, strengthened
        financial discipline, and operational expansion through strategic fuel
        storage and floating storage facilities.
      </p>

      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-block bg-white text-[#018FF5] font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition"
      >
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
